release_note: Improvements to text based item views. More text styling.
Polished UI. Use Apple Pencil to draw and annotate board content. Import annotations from PDF to board. Fixed note taking feature.
Hello there! This version comes with several fixes to Text item s Inspector. Also with few other improvements behind the scene.
In this version OhMyMind comes with some UI updates to canvas items. Also interaction with Item Inspector was improved.

Now you can: Zoom canvas to default scale 100 via top toolbar menu. Move to last visible card if you ve scrolled far from the visible cards via top toolbar menu. Also: Current zoom and position value of the canvas are saved and restored next time.
